## Overview

**Spendora Student Expense Tracker** is a polished multi-page finance website built for students to manage everyday money flow through dedicated sections for dashboard, transactions, budgets, goals, and analytics. Student-oriented finance tools commonly focus on simplifying expense logging, category control, reporting, and habit visibility so users can understand spending without a complicated workflow. [1][2][3]

The project follows a separate-page front-end structure, which is a common pattern in expense tracker websites because it keeps data entry, summaries, planning, and reporting easier to navigate and maintain. Multi-page separation is also regularly used in practical HTML/CSS/JavaScript finance tracker projects. [4][5][6]

***

