## Portfolio Description

**Spendora Student Expense Tracker** is a multi-page student finance website built with HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and Chart.js. It helps users manage income, expenses, budgets, savings goals, and analytics through a structured front-end architecture with separate page files and reusable shared styles. [11][6][12]

